'''Beit El Faqs'''  ({{lang-ar|بيت الفقس }})  is a [[Sunni Islam in Lebanon|Sunni Muslim]] Lebanese village<ref>{{cite web|title=Municipal and ikhtiyariah elections in Northern Lebanon|url=http://www.localiban.org/IMG/pdf/iiMonthly-Municip-Mar10-E92.pdf|publisher=The Monthly|accessdate=20 April 2015|page=8|date=March 2010|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160603040803/http://www.localiban.org/IMG/pdf/iiMonthly-Municip-Mar10-E92.pdf|archivedate=3 June 2016|df=}}</ref> located in the [[Miniyeh-Danniyeh District]] in the region of North Lebanon.

